<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩٤-<span style="color:#006d98"> قَالَ:</span> وَسَمِعْتُ عَبْدَ اللَّهِ يَقُولُ: لِلْمُزَاحِ عَشْرَةُ خصالٍ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">أَوَّلُهَا:</span> ذَهَابُ الْوَرَعِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالثَّانِي:</span> ذَهَابُ الْهَيْبَةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالثَّالِثُ:</span> ذَهَابُ الْبَهَاءِ مِنْ وَجْهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالرَّابِعَةُ:</span> فَسَادُ القلب.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#006d98">والخامس:</span> خيانة الجليس.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#006d98">والسادس:</span> أذاء الْحَفَظَةُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالسَّابِعُ:</span> يَهْدِمُ الصَّدَاقَةَ الْقَدِيمَةَ، وَيَبْنِي الْعَدَاوَةَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالثَّامِنُ:</span> يَذِمَّهُ الْعُقَلاءُ، وَيَسْخَرُ بِهِ السُّفُهَاءُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالتَّاسِعُ:</span> فَرَحُهُ قليلٌ، وَتَرَحُهُ طويلٌ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>⦗١٧٠⦘<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالْعَاشِرُ:</span> عَلَيْهِ وِزْرُ مَنِ اقْتَدَى بِهِ إِلَى يَوْمِ الْقِيَامَةِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>